OL,3,CMan crashes car into historic shelter
OL,4,Cand lake causing #90,000 of damage
OL,6,FA speeding driver caused #90,000 worth
OL,7,Fof damage to a Grade II-listed
OL,8,Fbandstand before plunging into the
OL,9,FMarine Lake.
OL,11,FHarry Mason, 30, smashed into the 120-
OL,12,Fyear-old Victorian bus shelter at the
OL,13,Fend of Albany Road after a 90mph
OL,14,Fpolice chase through Southport in the
OL,15,Fearly hours of 1 February 2025.
OL,17,FLiverpool Crown Court heard how the
OL,18,Fincident began when a police officer
OL,19,Fon Roe Lane saw a silver Mercedes
OL,20,Fcrash twice into the kerb and
OL,21,Fsignalled for it to stop.
