OL,7,Flosing sight of the Mercedes before
OL,8,Ffinding it submerged in the Marine
OL,9,FLake, after it had collided with the
OL,10,Fhistoric bandstand on the Promenade.
OL,12,FPictures of the sunken car quickly
OL,13,Fbegan circulating on Facebook, leading
OL,14,Fto Mason's girlfriend contacting
OL,15,FMerseyside Police after recognising it
OL,16,Fas hers.
OL,18,FMason later falsely reported the
OL,19,Fvehicle as stolen before admitting
OL,20,Fresponsibility.
