OL,6,FAlan Lake, project manager at Sefton
OL,7,FCouncil, said the damage to the
OL,8,Flandmark was "in the region of
OL,9,F#90,000".
OL,11,FHe said: "It's a much-loved, 120-year-
OL,12,Fold feature. The damage will impact on
OL,13,Fthe council's already stretched
OL,14,Fstaffing and financial resources.
OL,16,F"Unfortunately, precious resources
OL,17,Fwill have to be diverted to the
OL,18,Faftermath of an event which should
OL,19,Fnever have happened.
