OL,6,F"The town of Southport and our local
OL,7,Fcommunities, which cherish the town's
OL,8,Fhistorical architecture, have suffered
OL,9,Fa great loss. The shelter has stood
OL,10,Ffor 120 years; it survived two World
OL,11,FWars and until that night remained
OL,12,Fintact.
OL,14,F"The cost to repair this damage will
OL,15,Fbe in the region of #90k. At present,
OL,16,Fthe council simply cannot afford this
OL,17,Funless budget and resources are
OL,18,Fdiverted from other areas... This
OL,19,Fdamage was the result of one selfish
OL,20,Fperson."
