OL,6,FDefending, Damian Nolan said Mason had
OL,7,Frecently been made redundant and was
OL,8,Fstruggling with mental health
OL,9,Fdifficulties.
OL,11,F"He feared that his life as he knew it
OL,12,Fhad no further value," he said.
OL,14,F"He stupidly panicked and provided
OL,15,Fthat statement, but he had the good
OL,16,Fsense to remedy it and the true story
OL,17,Fcame out."
