OL,4,Cand lake causing #90,000 of damage
OL,6,FMason, of The Mallards, Southport,
OL,7,Fpleaded guilty to dangerous driving
OL,8,Fand perverting the course of justice.
OL,9,FHe was sentenced to 14 months in
OL,10,Fprison, suspended for two years, with
OL,11,F20 rehabilitation days, a four-month
OL,12,Fcurfew, and an 18-month driving ban.
